      "text": "This April, the Tower House was included in the list of protected historical building in Tokyo"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15400.0,
      "end_time": 18200.0,
      "text": "This is a triangular construction"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18200.0,
      "end_time": 21120.0,
      "text": "Which has been visited by many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21120.0,
      "end_time": 26040.0,
      "text": "Some famous architects have visited the house when they were students"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31520.0,
      "end_time": 34680.0,
      "text": "My name is Rie Azuma"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34680.0,
      "end_time": 39440.0,
      "text": "I’ve been an architect for more than 30 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39440.0,
      "end_time": 45760.0,
      "text": "There are 6 Hoshinoya hotels in Japan and abroad designed by me"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 47240.0,
      "end_time": 50560.0,
      "text": "My father is architect Takamitsu Azuma"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 50560.0,
      "end_time": 55400.0,
      "text": "The Tower House is the first piece of work of my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 58360.0,
      "text": "He was a bit over 30 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 58360.0,
      "end_time": 62600.0,
      "text": "The house was built in 1966"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 67360.0,
      "end_time": 72920.0,
      "text": "In the first few years, my father’s office was on the first floor of the building"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 72920.0,
      "end_time": 78280.0,
      "text": "He wanted to be able to walk to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 78280.0,
      "end_time": 82800.0,
      "text": "So living near his office became a reasonable choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 82800.0,
      "end_time": 87240.0,
      "text": "And he built the Tower House"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 89160.0,
      "end_time": 92280.0,
      "text": "The house was erected on a 20-square-meter plot of land"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 92280.0,
      "end_time": 93920.0,
      "text": "And the main area that can be used as rooms"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 93920.0,
      "end_time": 95960.0,
      "text": "Covers only 12 square meters"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 95960.0,
      "end_time": 98480.0,
      "text": "There are six levels, one underground and five above"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 98480.0,
      "end_time": 100680.0,
      "text": "The first floor is a garage"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 102840.0,
      "end_time": 106080.0,
      "text": "The second floor holds the living room, dining room and kitchen"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 109480.0,
      "end_time": 110760.0,
      "text": "My father would sit opposite to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 110760.0,
      "end_time": 112920.0,
      "text": "Mother and I would sit here"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 112920.0,
      "end_time": 116320.0,
      "text": "We’d move the chairs over and have meals here"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 116320.0,
      "end_time": 119800.0,
      "text": "Then put the chairs back"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 119800.0,
      "end_time": 122680.0,
      "text": "Into the living room"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 122680.0,
      "end_time": 127840.0,
      "text": "My mother used to cook here"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 127840.0,
      "end_time": 132040.0,
      "text": "She said that she could look outside while cooking here"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 133480.0,
      "end_time": 137880.0,
      "text": "The third floor is a void, a restroom and a bathroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 140960.0,
      "end_time": 143040.0,
      "text": "The fourth floor is the main bedroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 143040.0,
      "end_time": 146520.0,
      "text": "My parents slept here when we all lived here together"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 146520.0,
      "end_time": 151280.0,
      "text": "During weekend days there is light in the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 151280.0,
      "end_time": 152760.0,
      "text": "That’s very nice"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 152760.0,
      "end_time": 154200.0,
      "text": "I read in bed a lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 157520.0,
      "end_time": 160200.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 160200.0,
      "end_time": 165360.0,
      "text": "He left us three years ago at the age of 84"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 165360.0,
      "end_time": 168720.0,
      "text": "I used to have words with him all the time when I was a student"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 168720.0,
      "end_time": 172160.0,
      "text": "And we rarely communicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 172160.0,
      "end_time": 174360.0,
      "text": "But after we started working together"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 174360.0,
      "end_time": 177640.0,
      "text": "I’d learned a lot from him"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 180320.0,
      "end_time": 183960.0,
      "text": "The fifth floor is a child room and a balcony"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 183960.0,
      "end_time": 188000.0,
      "text": "It used to be my room when we first moved in"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 189640.0,
      "end_time": 192880.0,
      "text": "I would sit at my desk"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 192880.0,
      "end_time": 197640.0,
      "text": "And study while staring at the sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 203000.0,
      "end_time": 205240.0,
      "text": "There is no door in the Tower House"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 205240.0,
      "end_time": 207320.0,
      "text": "But it doesn’t make life inconvenient"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 207320.0,
      "end_time": 212240.0,
      "text": "When my mother came up to hang clothes on the balcony"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 212240.0,
      "end_time": 215120.0,
      "text": "The sound of her going up the stairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 215120.0,
      "end_time": 217840.0,
      "text": "Would give me a notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 217840.0,
      "end_time": 221760.0,
      "text": "Or when I was studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 221760.0,
      "end_time": 223680.0,
      "text": "And there were guests, or my parents were watching TV downstairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 223680.0,
      "end_time": 227280.0,
      "text": "I would yell “Keep it down please” if they were too loud"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 227280.0,
      "end_time": 230480.0,
      "text": "And when dinner was ready, they would call me from downstairs too"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 230720.0,
      "end_time": 234640.0,
      "text": "All our memories about family is stored in the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 234640.0,
      "end_time": 236920.0,
      "text": "For me, the Tower House is part of our family"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 236920.0,
      "end_time": 239640.0,
      "text": "It’s like a family member"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 242120.0,
      "end_time": 243840.0,
      "text": "What makes the Tower House stand out"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 243840.0,
      "end_time": 246800.0,
      "text": "Is that despite its limited site area"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 246800.0,
      "end_time": 249160.0,
      "text": "It feels spacious"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 249160.0,
      "end_time": 252320.0,
      "text": "There are some openings on the south side"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 252320.0,
      "end_time": 257280.0,
      "text": "Through these windows, you can see different scenes in different directions"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 257279.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263080.0,
      "text": "And as you go up the stairs, you will be showered in continuous new views"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 263080.0,
      "end_time": 264800.0,
      "text": "You won’t feel constrained at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 264800.0,
      "end_time": 266760.0,
      "text": "Although the house is right next to the streets"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 266760.0,
      "end_time": 269200.0,
      "text": "The walls sticking out"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 269200.0,
      "end_time": 272960.0,
      "text": "Is guarding the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 278640.0,
      "text": "The avenue outside was completed the same time as the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 278640.0,
      "end_time": 281880.0,
      "text": "You can feel the seasons in the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 281880.0,
      "end_time": 286280.0,
      "text": "This also enriches the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 289280.0,
      "end_time": 292440.0,
      "text": "I moved in at 6"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 292440.0,
      "end_time": 295000.0,
      "text": "And everything you see in the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 295000.0,
      "end_time": 297240.0,
      "text": "Is the same as fifty years ago except the faucets"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 299960.0,
      "end_time": 302960.0,
      "text": "I hope that we can understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 302960.0,
      "end_time": 310120.0,
      "text": "That our perception of space does not equal to its actual physical size"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 310120.0,
      "end_time": 314640.0,
      "text": "As the sense of space is not directly convertible to numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 314640.0,
      "end_time": 320040.0,
      "text": "So “how many square meters” shouldn’t be the sole consideration"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 320040.0,
      "end_time": 324520.0,
      "text": "Besides, building a house is not all about money"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 324520.0,
      "end_time": 327240.0,
      "text": "To build a good living space you need to put in thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 327240.0,
      "end_time": 331880.0,
      "text": "How to spend your money is an important question to answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 333520.0,
      "end_time": 338400.0,
      "text": "When you live in a house for 50 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 338400.0,
      "end_time": 344840.0,
      "text": "You would understand that there are things you can change, like furniture and home appliances"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 344840.0,
      "end_time": 347960.0,
      "text": "But there are also things you can’t change, like the basic structure of the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 347960.0,
      "end_time": 351040.0,
      "text": "If you have an interesting basic structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 351040.0,
      "end_time": 354880.0,
      "text": "You will have dozens of year of fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 357160.0,
      "end_time": 359640.0,
      "text": "My father once said that"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 359640.0,
      "end_time": 365680.0,
      "text": "When you live in a city, you won’t need every function in your house"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 365680.0,
      "end_time": 369360.0,
      "text": "Because the city could compensate for it"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 369360.0,
      "end_time": 372400.0,
      "text": "If you don’t have the space for a lot of books at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 372400.0,
      "end_time": 374840.0,
      "text": "You can go to the library nearby"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 374840.0,
      "end_time": 376840.0,
      "text": "If you have a small fridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 376840.0,
      "end_time": 379120.0,
      "text": "You can go to the grocery store everyday"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 379120.0,
      "end_time": 381600.0,
      "text": "You would have fresh ingredients all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 381600.0,
      "end_time": 386200.0,
      "text": "Living in a city"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 386200.0,
      "end_time": 392600.0,
      "text": "Is living with changes and new experiences"
    }
  ]
